        <mxCell id="fwtxt" value="Default → mgmt: operator-IP only · 22/443/6443/8006             · Default → cluster/dmz: NONE             · cluster → Default LAN: NONE (NAS isolated)&#10;mgmt → cluster: ALL                                              · mgmt → dmz: ALL                                              · cluster → mgmt: 53/123 only (DNS/NTP)&#10;cluster → dmz: 443→ingress, 7844→cloudflared                     · dmz → cluster: 443→ingress only                              · dmz → mgmt: NONE&#10;Internet → any lab VLAN: NONE (Cloudflare Tunnel only)            · any lab VLAN → Internet: as needed (egress filter is Phase 4)&#10;ZBF gotchas (see memory): rule-order within zone-pair · Local-In ≠ Inter-VLAN · Return-traffic needs explicit Established,Related rule in opposite direction" style="text;html=1;align=left;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=10;fontFamily=Courier New" vertex="1" parent="fwbox">
